WEBVTT

00:00:27.645 --> 00:00:34.108
Pa neka priča počne.

00:00:34.108 --> 00:00:39.046
Jedne mračne i olujne noći - doista -

00:00:39.046 --> 00:00:43.149
bilo je to 10. srpnja 1856. godine.

00:00:43.157 --> 00:00:45.101
Munje su obasjavale nebo,

00:00:45.101 --> 00:00:47.188
i jedno dijete se rodilo.

00:00:47.188 --> 00:00:50.196
Zvao se Nikola,

00:00:50.196 --> 00:00:51.840
Nikola Tesla.

00:00:51.840 --> 00:00:54.860
Dijete je odraslo u jednog jako pametnog čovjeka.

00:00:54.860 --> 00:00:57.004
Dopustite da vam pokažem.

00:00:57.004 --> 00:01:04.552
Tesla, koliko je 236 puta 501?